.com/avatar/bb35/5a05/550645_xlarge.png?m=1715408821", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb35/5a05/550645_xlarge.png?m=1715408821", "created": 1626061040, "last_modified": 1715408821}, "last_reply_by": "lovepocky", "last_touched": 1717830051, "title": "观《媳妇坐月子。。。。》有感，我敢说 95%的烟鬼不在乎别人感受", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1047883", "created": 1717813665, "deleted": 0, "content": "在厕所抽烟，在电梯抽烟，在阳台抽烟把烟头往下丢\r\n没有常识", "content_rendered": "<p>在厕所抽烟，在电梯抽烟，在阳台抽烟把烟头往下丢\n没有常识</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717814010, "replies": 52, "id": 1047883}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 11440, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991", "stars": 3386, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 8, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 651632, "username": "LTIT86", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/LTIT86", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1e2d7f35d737af6b52323771f3ff6e8a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1e2d7f35d737af6b52323771f3ff6e8a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1e2d7f35d737af6b52323771f3ff6e8a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1695884077, "last_modified": 1695884077}, "last_reply_by": "LTIT86", "last_touched": 1717827743, "title": "玩了一段时间《鸣潮》后，我突然理解了为啥 iPhone 不上均热板", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1047794", "created": 1717758263, "deleted": 0, "content": "双持苹果 13 和小米 14 玩《鸣潮》一周多后，发现手机散热也不是越强游戏体验就越好。\r\n\r\n在开同样的画质和帧数限制下，两台手机的发热表现，不，因该说发热行为不同：\r\n\r\n小米 14 在开始游戏两三分钟后就能通过手掌感觉到发热了，在游戏十多分钟后本人已经感觉手机热到影响握持了，但是此时的游戏依旧能流畅运行；\r\n苹果 13 的表现则是在游戏开始的十多分钟里并没有感觉到机身升温迅速，直到游戏开始卡顿时机身开始变得烫手；\r\n\r\n两者一次游戏的时间相差并不大，小米 14 是机身热到必须放下，苹果 13 是游戏帧数不稳定也需要休息。\r\n\r\n总结：苹果不上均热板很大的可能是认为手机这种设备并不需要长时间的高性能释放，亦或者说手持设备并不适合长时间的高性能释放。", "content_rendered": "<p>双持苹果 13 和小米 14 玩《鸣潮》一周多后，发现手机散热也不是越强游戏体验就越好。</p>\n<p>在开同样的画质和帧数限制下，两台手机的发热表现，不，因该说发热行为不同：</p>\n<p>小米 14 在开始游戏两三分钟后就能通过手掌感觉到发热了，在游戏十多分钟后本人已经感觉手机热到影响握持了，但是此时的游戏依旧能流畅运行；\n苹果 13 的表现则是在游戏开始的十多分钟里并没有感觉到机身升温迅速，直到游戏开始卡顿时机身开始变得烫手；</p>\n<p>两者一次游戏的时间相差并不大，小米 14 是机身热到必须放下，苹果 13 是游戏帧数不稳定也需要休息。</p>\n<p>总结：苹果不上均热板很大的可能是认为手机这种设备并不需要长时间的高性能释放，亦或者说手持设备并不适合长时间的高性能释放。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717758343, "replies": 52, "id": 1047794}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 3905, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927", "stars": 1244, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 544482, "username": "FishStars", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/FishStars", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_mini.png?m=1659520115", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_normal.png?m=1659520115", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_large.png?m=1659520115", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_xlarge.png?m=1659520115", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_xlarge.png?m=1659520115", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1cf7/bbdf/544482_xlarge.png?m=1659520115", "created": 1620189848, "last_modified": 1659520115}, "last_reply_by": "aliceclark", "last_touched":